## Fridge Rule Evidence

This scene directly confirms the clarified standalone-fridge rule:

- Use the existing refrigerator component from available components.
- Keep it in the scene when it represents the real appliance/visual check.
- Do not create a separate measuring object for the niche.
- Verify adjacent panels, clearances, and surrounding module placement against the actual fridge component bbox.

## Upper Row And Filler Pattern

Upper row uses tall `TC1` modules in two Z bands:

- Lower upper band: `TC1-H1`, `TC1HL`, `TC1HL#1` at `Z[1500..2138]`.
- Top band: `TC1#1/#2/#3/#6/#7` at `Z[2138..2505]`.
