- Width sequence: `50`, `392`, `392`, `50`, `805`, `805`, `19`, `782`, `19`, `600`, `19`.

Pattern: upper cabinets can be a two-band composition with separate top-lift/antresol modules. The generator must not collapse this into one row of standard uppers.

